    "summary": "Booking.com exposes two documented public developer APIs: Connectivity APIs (machine-account auth via JWT Bearer or legacy Basic) and the Demand API (affiliate ID + token), plus the Data Portability API (OAuth/DMA scope); no MCP server or standalone CLI was confirmed.",
